SUMMARY:Sat/ April 11: "Fantasy Life"  (Drama)
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Movies & Social Group - Celebrating 14 Years!\n*Hi eve
 ryone- this 'last-minute' film announcement is for a new film opening up t
 his w/e that looks quite good! 😃*\n\n**Plot Summary :** *"After losing 
 his job\, Sam Stein suffers a panic attack and stumbles into a job babysit
 ting his psychiatrists three grand-daughters..." (Pls see online for more 
 details!)*\n\n**Starring:** Mathew Shear\, Amanda Peet\, Allesandro Nivola
 \, Bob Balabon\, Judd Hirsch\, Andrea Martin\, Jessica Harper (& others)\n
 \n**Director:** **Mathew Shear**\n\n**Trailer:** Pls see on Cineplex.com w
 ebsite or online for this film!\n\n**What time the Meetup group will meet 
 at:** suggest **@7:00-7:05pm**\n\n**Time the movie STARTS:** **7:10pm**\n\
 n**Movie Running Time:** approx. 1 hr & 31min\n\n**Meetup Spot:** I will b
 e standing in front of the row of movie posters close to the escalators an
 d I will be carrying my infamous ***"Leopard-Spotted Purse" with 'Red Stra
 ps'!*** I'll be there between **@7:00-7:05pm** then I'll head inside with 
 the "group".... I'll also send out my 'cell #" to any RSVPs that I see in 
 case anyone needs to contact me who might be running a bit 'late'\, etc...
 \n\n**How to Find the Theatre:** You have to enter through the Manulife Ce
 ntre build on Bloor Street (55 Bloor street W). It is up stairs from the I
 ndigo Book store .\n\n**Where I will be sitting:** I will be in Seat **F-9
 ! 😃**\n\n**Cost of movie:** This is listed on the Cineplex website ('ad
 ult'/ Senior \, etc) .....You are responsible for buying your own ticket. 
 You also will not be able to sign up if you have not bought your ticket as
  it is reserve seating.\n\n**Click here to go to the website to buy your t
 icket:** [https://www.cineplex.com/](https://www.cineplex.com/)\n\n**After
  the Movie:** We'll do a quick 'check-in' back at the original 'meet-up' s
 pot & for those who'd like to go out for a quick bite/drink & chat more ab
 out the film ....\, we'll head out shortly after!!\n\n**PLEASE NOTE:** Tic
 ket must be bought before signing up. You will be asked where you will be 
 sitting. Seating is very limited.\n*Don't forget to join Cineplex's new MO
 VIE CLUB for those that love movies and discounts* - [https://www.cineplex
 .com/cineclub](https://www.cineplex.com/cineclub)\n\n**NOTE:** All movies 
 are subject to change\, I will always try for the best time\, and to see a
  movie in 2D (some movies are a must in 3D) for the best price. \\*\\*\\*A
 lso\, please keep an eye out for any changes in venue or movie times. \\*\
 \*\n**I look forward to seeing you there!!**\n\n**REMEMBER YOU CAN JUST SI
 GN UP ON THE DAY OF OR JUST SHOW UP ON THE DAY OF IF YOU ARE NOT SURE YOU 
 CAN MAKE IT.**\n\n**THIS GROUP IS OPEN TO THOSE THAT WANT TO BE SOCIAL\, M
 AKE FRIENDS\, THAT ARE SINGLE OR NOT SINGLE. WE ALSO HAVE LOTS OF OTHER EV
 ENTS LIKE\, MOVIES\, WALKS\, HIKES\, ARTS & CULTURE AND RESTAURANTS. WE LO
 VE TO SUPPORT MEMEBERS TO SOCIALIZE AND TO FORM LONG LASTING FRIENDSHIPS.*
 *\n\n**Toronto Movies and Social Group: Policy**\n\nPlease do not use your
  cellphone\, talk\, or otherwise disrupt the enjoyment of others around yo
 u\, once the movie starts. Any complaints will be dealt with first as a wa
 rning\, then subsequent removal from the group on repeated complaints.\n\n
 **Rules:** [Click Here!](https://www.meetup.com/toronto-movies-and-social-
 group/events/293241263/)\n**Getting The Best Out Of Meet:** [Click Here!](
 https://www.meetup.com/toronto-movies-and-social-group/events/293241269/)\
 n\nDon't Forget to join our email list (Meetup does not send out emails to
 \neveryone in a group) to get our weekly news later about upcoming events:
  [http://eepurl.com/hKt76f](http://eepurl.com/hKt76f)\n\nFacebook group @ 
 [http://www.facebook.com/groups/502945113062739/](http://www.facebook.com/
 groups/502945113062739/)\n\n**Scene card:** A Scene card helps you to coll
 ect movie points at Cineplex movie theatres. After 1000 points or 10 movie
 s your 11th movie is free. If you love to see movies then this is a must h
 ave card. Go to - [https://www.scene.ca](https://www.scene.ca/) to get you
 r card today\n\n**Laura😊** is the organizer for this meetup. If you nee
 d to contact her\, please post a message on the wall\, or message her thru
  Meetup!
